[/quote]lol? the highest and less laggiest go on the list. so, make sure you have good ram [i perfer the new 3G] and VERY good internet![/quote]

that isnt nessicarily true, some servers are very very very laggy and get put on the list, just wait till the server status page updates, if it isnt on then, yours hasn’t been recinised yet. And you dont always need a good internet. I have a slower then most server makers internet but i have over 150000 kb of ram. You can also have very good internet and low ram. Welcome
